{"word":"G1822 - ἐξαρτίζω - exartízō - ex-ar-tid'-zo - Accomplish","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ἐξαρτίζω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">exartízō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">ex-ar-tid'-zo</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Accomplish</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - நிறைவேற்று, தகுதி உள்ளவனாகு"},{"paragraph":"to complete, finish"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1537 - ἐκ - ek - ek/1537\">G1537</a> and a derivative of <a href=\"#/G739 - ἄρτιος - ártios - ar'-tee-os/739\">G739</a>; to <i>finish out</i> (time); figuratively to <i>equip fully</i> (a teacher): - accomplish, thoroughly furnish.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1822/1822\">G1822</a>, <a href=\"#/G2675/2675\">G2675</a>, <a href=\"#/G2676/2676\">G2676</a>, <a href=\"#/G2677/2677\">G2677</a>, <a href=\"#/G739/739\">G739</a>"}]}